HEADWORD: Stogy
<hw>Sto"gy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Etym. uncertain. Cf.
<er>Stocky</er>.]</ety> <def>heavy; coarse; clumsy.</def>
<mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
